---
description: Always keep plugin version and manual changelog synchronized
alwaysApply: true
---

For every change in this repository, keep release metadata in sync unless the user explicitly says not to.

Required updates:

1) Bump plugin version (patch increment by default):
- `user-manager.php` plugin header: `Version: x.y.z`
- `includes/class-user-manager-core.php`: `const VERSION = 'x.y.z';`

2) Add/update release notes for that same version in both places:
- Top changelog block in `user-manager.php`
- Top entry in `includes/tabs/class-user-manager-tab-versions.php`

3) Keep version number and release date consistent across all version/changelog locations.

